               boolean ring,
               boolean center,
               java.lang.String rotate,
               double fudge,
               double verticalShift)
        Create a new protein given a pdb file + insane parameters.
        Parameters:
        errorMessages - the list to add error messages to
        fileLocation - the location of the pdb file
        grid - the grid for this simulation
        ring - boolean: is the protein ring shaped?
        center - boolean: center the protein?
        rotate - rotate the protein (princ|random|#angle)
        fudge - the fudge factor for lipid-protein overlap.
        verticalShift - the vertical shift of the protein
